array.string: Diners pluck sushi & maki rolls from a moving conveyor belt at this Japan-based chain outpost.
Japanese teppanyaki-style eatery where chefs prepare steak & seafood at tableside grills.
Stylish choice for sushi & Japanese small plates plus a broad sake selection in sleek, vibrant digs.
Family-friendly chain for seafood & American fare served in a fishing-boat-themed setting.
Sprawling food court with an array of Japanese dishes, a French restaurant & an indoor beer garden.
